data.description: Explore this captivating two-story home tucked away in the Star Ranch neighborhood. Featuring a spacious floor plan with high ceilings and a ton of natural light throughout. The open-concept kitchen includes a central island with comfortable seating, along with recessed lighting and plenty of storage space. The primary bedroom suite offers a dual vanity, walk-in shower with a bench, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find a large game room and an additional bedroom thoughtfully arranged. Step outside to a private backyard with an oversized back patio, creating an ideal space for outdoor entertainment. This exceptional property is a must-see in a vibrant and welcoming community!
